# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Description
# -----------
#
# Use Emacs PEL facilities to start Emacs in Graphical mode, log its startup
# time and then turn Emacs off.
#
# Requirements:  ge :
#                - a script or shell alias that starts Emacs in Graphical mode.


# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Script
# ------
#
#
ge -e pel-log-init-time -e kill-emacs


# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
